          <h2>Artistic Philosophy</h2>
          <p>Madison believes in opera as a living, breathing art form that can connect with audiences of all
            backgrounds. Each production seeks to illuminate the emotional core of a work while creating visually
            stunning and dramatically compelling theater.</p>

